task.summary: Added AES encryption that is read from a file with a list of siteIDs and AES keys (IncomingReadingDecryptor class). Added BaseStation class that reads a config file and producers an object that starts sending readings to a specified server. Also Fixed the SensorReadingSender so that when connection drops, uses exponential back off before trying again and returns after either a reading is sent (with true) or after a specified number of attempts (around 30 minutes currently).

Added AES encryption that is read from a file with a list of siteIDs and AES keys (IncomingReadingDecryptor class). Added BaseStation class that reads a config file and producers an object that starts sending readings to a specified server. Also Fixed the SensorReadingSender so that when connection drops, uses exponential back off before trying again and returns after either a reading is sent (with true) or after a specified number of attempts (around 30 minutes currently).
Moved parser from server side to client side. Created a DBEntryToStringConverter object to facilitate this conversion

Working on account manager command line tool. So far have set up a load of text files that are read in and displayed to the user. Create a command line tool that sets this up. Created a UserHandlerGenerator that reads in a config file and then you give it a prefix and it returns an object specified by name in the config file. Similarly creates a ResourceFileReader that gives you an array of the lines of text for a specified prefix
CommandLineTool now instead of crashing when components throw exception, displays to screen as an error message, and goes back to selection screen
